rows.label: qst200401_msg0001
rows.name: Oi, Ellenora! Time to pay up!

rows.label: qst200401_msg0002
rows.name:
I-I'm sorry... But please,
just a little more time...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0003
rows.name: Oi, oi, I'm sick of hearing that line.

rows.label: qst200401_msg0004
rows.name:
How long are you going
to make us wait? Huh?

rows.label: qst200401_msg0005
rows.name:
I-I really don't have the
money... I'm begging you...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0006
rows.name: Hah? We can't wait any longer either.

rows.label: qst200401_msg0007
rows.name:
If you can't pay, you can't pay.
We've got our own ideas...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0009
rows.name: Yeah, we can't just let this happen...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0013
rows.name: I don't need to take orders from you!

rows.label: qst200401_msg0015
rows.name:
This guy... he's strong...
We're no match for him...

rows.label: qst200401_msg0016
rows.name:
I will say it once more.
Get out of here...
